<section class="py-20 bg-[#F7F3EE] border-t border-[#F1EBE4]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <div class="mb-10">
            <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif mb-4 text-[#544A40]">
                公式LINEで気軽に相談・予約
            </h2>
            <div
                class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 text-[#A88B58] text-[10px] md:text-xs tracking-[0.2em] font-serif uppercase"
            >
                <div class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-[#A88B58]/30"></div>
                LINE Contact
                <div class="h-[1px] w-8 bg-[#A88B58]/30"></div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mb-10 text-sm md:text-base leading-loose text-[#6B5F54] max-w-2xl mx-auto font-serif">
            <span class="inline-block">「体験レッスンを予約したい」</span><span class="inline-block">「うちの地域は出張可能？」</span><span class="inline-block">「電子ピアノしか持っていなくても大丈夫？」など、</span><br class="hidden md:inline" />
            <span class="inline-block">些細なご質問でも</span><span class="inline-block">お気軽にお問い合わせください。</span>
            <span class="inline-block">1対1のトークで</span><span class="inline-block">講師が直接お答えします。</span>
        </p>

        <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-2">
            <a
                href="https://lin.ee/QL31tIZ"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="inline-flex items-center justify-center bg-[#06C755] hover:bg-[#05b04b] text-white px-8 md:px-12 py-4.5 rounded-full font-bold shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:-translate-y-0.5 tracking-[0.2em] text-sm w-full max-w-md gap-2 line_click_mid_cta"
            >
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="w-5 h-5 fill-current" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <path d="M22 10.02c0-4.428-4.486-8.02-10-8.02S2 5.592 2 10.02c0 3.966 3.23 7.284 7.6 7.907.296.064.697.195.797.447.091.229.06.588.029.842-.116.892-.375 2.564-.427 2.9-.06.398.146.365.309.244.152-.113 2.454-1.619 3.456-2.319.721.2 1.488.31 2.236.31 5.514 0 10-3.593 10-8.021z"/>
                </svg>
                公式LINEで相談してみる
            </a>
            <span class="text-[10px] text-[#6B5F54]/70 mt-2">※クリックするとLINE友だち追加画面が開きます</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
